				<h1>Electric Cycle</h1>
				<p>An electric cycle, or e-bike, is a bicycle equipped with an electric motor that assists with pedaling. This motor is powered by a rechargeable battery, providing extra speed and reducing effort, especially on inclines. E-bikes are eco-friendly, offering an alternative to cars for short-distance commuting.
				 They come in various designs, including mountain and city bikes, catering to different needs. With growing popularity, electric cycles are revolutionizing urban mobility, offering a sustainable and efficient transportation option.
</p>
